WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.293
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.293 --> 00:00:03.691
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.691 --> 00:00:05.680
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:09.866
Well, it's Diana, my beautiful bride, and me.

00:00:10.471 --> 00:00:12.259
We're excited to be here today.

00:00:12.259 --> 00:00:16.409
I try to embarrass her as much as I can when she's sitting next to me.

00:00:17.618 --> 00:00:21.424
You don't know how many times we do these takes, and I try to be funny.

00:00:21.696 --> 00:00:24.080
I told her, "It's making her laugh.

00:00:29.199 --> 00:00:33.040
" If you can't have fun doing what you're doing, then why do it, right?

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:34.200
It's exciting times.

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:36.400
This is what Jesus is talking to us about.

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:41.680
Nothing is going to happen in the natural unless we pray it through in the spiritual first.

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:45.680
We must intercede and pray for what's coming.

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:47.360
He talked about it even today.

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:51.680
I was driving around, and Diana had to go into the grocery store.

00:00:52.057 --> 00:00:59.828
The Lord started talking about cars, people driving around in their cars, and the cars looking like they were on fire when the glory was on them.

00:00:59.828 --> 00:01:02.182
He said, "Brandon, I'm going to do something very unusual.

00:01:02.182 --> 00:01:03.840
" And I said, "Lord, what is that?

00:01:03.840 --> 00:01:08.720
" He said, "The fire was on buildings last time whenever Azusa Street happened.

00:01:09.291 --> 00:01:15.380
People saw fire on the buildings when Rodney Howard-Browne held meetings in Fort Worth, Texas.

00:01:15.380 --> 00:01:20.915
The building looked like it was on fire, and the fire department came, but the building was not on fire.

00:01:20.915 --> 00:01:25.617
It was on fire with the Holy Ghost, and they were seeing in the spirit realm a building that was on fire.

00:01:25.866 --> 00:01:36.000
" The Lord told me, "Brandon, what I'm about to do is that when people are driving around on the streets, it's going to look like their car is on fire.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:43.740
I'm going to show up in their car as they're interceding, driving around the city, and your car is going to look like you're on fire.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:56.829
People are going to be staring, thinking your car is on fire, as a sign and a wonder in these last days—not just on buildings, but on you when you walk in like Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego.

00:01:56.829 --> 00:01:59.160
You're in a Holy Ghost fire.

00:01:59.160 --> 00:02:01.020
They were in an actual fire.

00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:05.864
But I'm talking about a real fire that they see on us.

00:02:06.096 --> 00:02:09.040
They will go, 'What is going on with that guy?

00:02:09.040 --> 00:02:10.480
He's on fire.

00:02:10.480 --> 00:02:11.920
' It's the glory.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:12.400
It's the glory.

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:21.920
" Ladies and gentlemen, it's time to anticipate the demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God.

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:29.240
Over the past 30 or 40 years, or whatever you've had in your life, the Lord has shown me, He said, "Brandon, it's been a cultivation with folks.

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:35.440
Not everybody is going to walk in the greater supernatural miracles because they're not there yet.

00:02:35.440 --> 00:02:37.609
They'll try to take the glory for it.

00:02:37.609 --> 00:02:38.697
Do you understand?

00:02:38.697 --> 00:02:45.938
God will use you in an unusual way if you know how to deflect the glory to Him.

00:02:47.396 --> 00:02:55.760
" The Lord told me, "If you don't take the glory, Brandon, I'll use you to do great and mighty things.

00:02:56.160 --> 00:03:01.510
As long as you always deflect it like a mirror, deflecting the glory to Him.

00:03:01.510 --> 00:03:03.390
You attract to deflect.

00:03:03.390 --> 00:03:08.708
As long as you deflect the glory in these last days, I'll use you mightily.

00:03:08.708 --> 00:03:12.907
" "But there are many people who will not deflect it.

00:03:12.907 --> 00:03:14.239
They'll try to take it.

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:17.760
And He said, 'I will not share my glory with any man.

00:03:17.760 --> 00:03:24.613
' For what I'm about to do in these last days, no one has ever seen what's about to happen.

00:03:24.613 --> 00:03:32.605
No eye has seen, no ear has heard, nor has it entered into the heart of man the things that God has prepared for those that love Him.

00:03:32.605 --> 00:03:43.440
Listen, ladies and gentlemen, God is about to show up and show off in your life in an unprecedented way that's going to be shock and awe.

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:47.330
But He will not share His glory with what's about to take place.

00:03:47.330 --> 00:03:53.805
And if He can trust you to deflect it as a general, then He'll use you mightily.

00:03:55.019 --> 00:03:59.618
" He showed me it's going to be like a change in command in the natural, like we have in the army.

00:04:00.331 --> 00:04:04.742
We have the generals, then it goes to lieutenant generals, and it keeps going down, right?

00:04:05.097 --> 00:04:10.190
The Lord showed me that it is just like that in the spirit realm.

00:04:10.190 --> 00:04:14.640
And the ones that pay the price and are willing to say, "I deflect.

00:04:16.240 --> 00:04:17.710
Father, it's not me.

00:04:17.710 --> 00:04:18.250
It's You.

00:04:18.250 --> 00:04:23.909
" I just want everybody to know immediately when you're in a crowd and you're on fire with the glory, it's all about Jesus.

00:04:23.909 --> 00:04:26.560
This isn't about attracting attention to me.

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:28.390
This isn't about how great I am.

00:04:28.390 --> 00:04:29.830
It's about how great He is.

00:04:29.830 --> 00:04:32.040
He's able to operate through this vessel.

00:04:35.120 --> 00:04:42.430
Ladies and gentlemen, I have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power may be of Him and not of me.

00:04:42.430 --> 00:04:43.600
This is important.

00:04:43.600 --> 00:05:01.804
With what we're about to see—when we see the legs, the arms, the ears, and the dead being raised—we must remember we have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of me.

00:05:01.804 --> 00:05:04.352
I decrease, He increases.

00:05:04.624 --> 00:05:12.145
As long as we have a heart where He is increasing and we are decreasing, we are deflecting and looking at Him.

00:05:12.145 --> 00:05:14.647
He is the potter, I am the clay.

00:05:15.813 --> 00:05:16.880
He is not sharing His glory with anyone.

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:22.263
He could use anybody, but He's not sharing the glory.

00:05:23.086 --> 00:05:25.740
It's all about Him and nothing about me.

00:05:25.740 --> 00:05:28.296
I'm just a vessel that He uses in these end times.

00:05:28.296 --> 00:05:29.428
Do you understand?

00:05:29.428 --> 00:05:33.131
We attract to deflect, and it's very important.

00:05:33.394 --> 00:05:47.520
The Lord showed me today that as we are getting ready to see demonstrations and manifestations like we've never seen before, He said, "If you want to be a general in my army, know that I will not share my glory with anybody.

00:05:48.930 --> 00:05:50.479
" People will say, "Well, look at him.

00:05:50.479 --> 00:05:51.302
He's on fire.

00:05:51.302 --> 00:05:52.400
Can you believe that?

00:05:52.640 --> 00:05:57.280
Did you know that Sister Diana has raised 30 people from the dead?

00:05:57.280 --> 00:06:00.400
Boy, she's something, isn't she?

00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:02.960
" She's a child of the King, and I'm a child of the King.

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:08.960
We're all just doing exactly what He's called us to do, and He can use anybody.

00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:11.360
Keep your eyes on Him and stay focused.

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:12.936
It's important that you do this.

00:06:12.936 --> 00:06:17.919
You need to hear me because of what He's told me is coming.

00:06:17.919 --> 00:06:25.863
Unusual signs and wonders beyond anybody's comprehension are about to take place in the body of Christ.

00:06:25.863 --> 00:06:34.319
Unusual demonstrations, unusual miracles, things we've never seen before.

00:06:34.675 --> 00:06:43.530
If God showed up with the glory on Moses's face, He said, "Brandon, I'm going to show up with even greater glory on you.

00:06:43.530 --> 00:06:47.600
Watch if you learn to deflect.

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:48.400
" Keep learning.

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:50.000
Keep dying to self.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:52.120
That's why the Apostle Paul said, "I die daily.

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:54.759
" I will not take the glory.

00:06:54.759 --> 00:07:00.759
When the shadow of Peter walked down through wherever the people were sick, the glory touched them.

00:07:01.750 --> 00:07:05.405
He didn't even have to lay hands on them; the glory of the Lord touched these people, right?

00:07:06.639 --> 00:07:06.899
The shadow touched them.

00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:10.000
When the shadow touched them, it was the glory.

00:07:10.391 --> 00:07:12.160
It wasn't him; it was just a shadow.

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:21.640
The glory was radiating out of him so strongly and so powerfully that even the shadow touched them.

00:07:23.550 --> 00:07:27.646
That's what the Lord showed me during my prayer time all day today, just driving around.

00:07:28.980 --> 00:07:33.244
He said, "Brandon, you must keep this in mind all the time.

00:07:33.244 --> 00:07:40.040
You have a treasure in an earthen vessel, that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of you.

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:47.626
" This treasure that you carry—He said, "You don't share your treasure until I tell you to share it.

00:07:47.626 --> 00:07:49.901
It's not your gift.

00:07:49.901 --> 00:07:53.772
It's my gift being distributed through you.

00:07:53.772 --> 00:07:57.360
The gold and the silver are mine.

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:58.777
The cattle are mine.

00:07:58.777 --> 00:08:01.404
The anointing and the glory are mine.

00:08:04.426 --> 00:08:10.148
" This endless treasure that you carry in earthen vessels is a treasure.

00:08:10.536 --> 00:08:15.429
The power of the Holy Spirit is a treasure in an earthen vessel.

00:08:15.429 --> 00:08:18.160
And He showed me a vast supply.

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:21.131
And He said, "The supply will never run dry, Brandon.

00:08:42.099 --> 00:08:46.528
It will never run dry with anything that I've called you to do.

00:08:46.528 --> 00:08:48.112
There is a vast supply.

00:08:48.112 --> 00:08:49.413
" Come to the river.

00:08:49.413 --> 00:08:49.928
Hallelujah.

00:08:56.960 --> 00:08:57.120
I feel the Holy Spirit right now.

00:09:11.119 --> 00:09:22.537
He showed me this treasure and all these coins, and He said, "Just because you have it and you operate in it, Brandon, doesn't mean it's for you to just do what you want to do with it.

00:09:23.474 --> 00:09:27.413
" You are a steward of what I've called you to do.

00:09:27.413 --> 00:09:32.800
Listen, you are a steward of the money, of the wealth, of the glory.

00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:34.199
That's what I want to say.

00:09:43.060 --> 00:09:43.250
The vast supply, the treasure in earthen vessels.

00:09:44.064 --> 00:09:50.880
You have that treasure inside of you, ladies and gentlemen, and you're a steward of it.

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:54.640
'What do you want me to do with this, Lord?

00:09:54.640 --> 00:10:02.533
' And He said, 'You don't let everybody touch the treasure, and you don't tell everybody about it.

00:10:02.533 --> 00:10:04.754
' Because it's precious.

00:10:08.011 --> 00:10:08.526
The way you guard it and you protect it.

00:10:10.959 --> 00:10:21.451
And as you distribute it, you distribute the coins out—the treasure in earthen vessels—you distribute those out to the people that He tells you to.

00:10:27.067 --> 00:10:30.560
This is exactly what I've asked you to do today.

00:10:30.560 --> 00:10:34.862
Jesus said, 'I do nothing unless my Father instructs me to do it.

00:10:34.862 --> 00:10:39.270
' Even if He thought, 'Well, I'm the Son of God.

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:41.897
Are you kidding me?

00:10:47.467 --> 00:10:48.053
I can do whatever I want to do.

00:10:48.053 --> 00:10:50.659
Are you kidding me?

00:10:50.659 --> 00:10:51.440
I'm Jesus.

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:55.200
' No, He went about it even more humbled and dead to self.

00:10:55.200 --> 00:11:02.480
'I do nothing unless I hear my Father tell me to do it,' regardless of what He thought or what He could have done.

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:06.034
'I only do what I'm instructed to by my Father.

00:11:06.034 --> 00:11:13.893
' And that's exactly how He operated the whole time He was walking underneath the glory, and that's what we should do.

00:11:13.893 --> 00:11:20.720
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, and it's coins.

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:21.573
It's beautiful gold.

00:11:21.573 --> 00:11:22.427
It's beautiful diamonds.

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:28.529
What do you do with that in distributing it out to the people?

00:11:28.529 --> 00:11:31.920
Only do what the Father tells you to do.

00:11:39.340 --> 00:11:50.987
I have a treasure, and in these scriptures that He gives me today, the excellency of the power will be known to Him.

00:11:50.987 --> 00:11:59.760
I attract to deflect, and I always make sure I'm never going to share the glory with the Lord.

00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:01.947
It's all about Him and nothing about me.

00:12:01.947 --> 00:12:02.524
Does that make sense?

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:10.080
You have to keep this in your heart.

00:12:10.080 --> 00:12:13.973
He said, 'Those that do this, I will use even greater.

00:12:13.973 --> 00:12:18.319
They'll be ranked in the military in the spiritual realm.

00:12:18.319 --> 00:12:20.600
' Who will be used?

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:40.660
He said, 'There's a lot of them I will not be able to trust because the moment of fame, the moment of clout, when they start getting huge on YouTube, huge on the news, or Daystar calls you up, or whoever—"Hey, my goodness, we heard you raised five people from the dead!

00:12:40.660 --> 00:12:45.280
" Well, of course, don't you know how much time I've spent fasting and praying?

00:12:57.440 --> 00:12:57.714
Don't you know how much I've done?

00:12:57.714 --> 00:12:59.360
' It's all about Jesus.

00:13:07.179 --> 00:13:07.349
I just need you to know this.

00:13:07.349 --> 00:13:10.880
This is what He's instructing me today.

00:13:25.120 --> 00:13:25.493
And it was very beautiful, but it was talking about how it was going to be in the days ahead, just right here in front of us.

00:13:25.493 --> 00:13:26.907
Glory to God.

00:13:26.907 --> 00:13:27.573
Hallelujah!

00:13:27.573 --> 00:13:31.617
I'm so thankful for a praying wife, that we seek Him together.

00:13:31.617 --> 00:13:41.497
I'm telling you, it is so important to pray and to seek Him together with your spouse, and that's why you don't hook yourself up with a dead horse.

00:13:41.497 --> 00:13:45.520
'Well, I'm going to pray and get that person saved.

00:13:45.520 --> 00:13:48.399
I'm going to do this.

00:13:48.399 --> 00:13:51.360
I'm going to do that.

00:13:51.360 --> 00:13:52.170
' No.

00:13:52.170 --> 00:13:55.371
Do not marry and be unequally yoked with unbelievers.

00:13:55.371 --> 00:13:59.982
Find a believing believer if you're going to get married, or don't get married at all.

00:13:59.982 --> 00:14:04.389
You need to find a believing believer to get married to.

00:14:04.389 --> 00:14:08.000
I'm telling you, there's a lot of seeker-friendly...

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:15.988
You're going to see people that think, 'Well, we have to change things on the stage.

00:14:15.988 --> 00:14:19.279
We have to change things because we're losing numbers.

00:14:19.279 --> 00:14:20.651
We have to keep relevant.

00:14:20.651 --> 00:14:23.804
We have to do these things.

00:14:23.804 --> 00:14:26.000
' And, 'We have to change our stage.

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:29.484
We have to change our packaging because we're losing the people.

00:14:29.484 --> 00:14:41.180
' And the Lord told me, He said, 'Brandon, if you're standing in the middle of a field in a cow patty pasture, and you see poop all over the place, but people are gathered up...

00:14:41.180 --> 00:14:43.820
If I be lifted up, I'll draw all men unto me.

00:14:43.820 --> 00:14:59.725
' If the glory is there, I don't care if you're standing in waist-high mud, you're going to attract people like moths to a light, like these stupid flies flying around here trying to get around this light right now that I keep trying to kill.

00:14:59.725 --> 00:15:09.360
I'm telling you, if He be lifted up, regardless of what it is, what people are attracted to is not how pretty your stage is or how great your music is.

00:15:09.360 --> 00:15:10.960
It's the glory.

00:15:10.960 --> 00:15:12.560
It's the glory!

00:15:12.560 --> 00:15:15.360
I've seen it.

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:21.378
Even when Reinhard Bonnke did his meetings and crusades in Africa, four or five million people showed up, right?

00:15:21.378 --> 00:15:27.920
But he had just a little tractor-trailer and this little stage with this backdrop, nothing really cool.

00:15:27.920 --> 00:15:37.564
But the presence of the Lord was there, and you don't have to dress up anything when the presence of the Lord is there.

00:15:37.564 --> 00:15:43.658
They're just coming to see somebody burn, to be on fire for Jesus.

00:15:43.658 --> 00:15:53.680
But a lot of people who are dead spiritually try to dress it up really pretty and put a bow on it and think it's the glory, and it's not.

00:16:04.102 --> 00:16:06.470
And you're going to see what was once alive in the body of Christ—before that was an oasis in the desert—become a cesspool because they've cut themselves off from the vine.

00:16:06.470 --> 00:16:08.329
They are no longer attached.

00:16:10.240 --> 00:16:12.000
And it's happening more and more and more, from what I hear.

00:16:14.331 --> 00:16:14.686
And you go, 'What happened?

00:16:14.686 --> 00:16:16.160
They were a place of refreshing.

00:16:16.160 --> 00:16:26.399
' They detached themselves, and now they try to decorate it and make it look pretty because it's work to get on the vine.

00:16:29.319 --> 00:16:30.339
It's work to die to self, and they don't want to do that.

00:16:30.339 --> 00:16:33.480
They go, 'Well, I don't want to do that.

00:16:33.480 --> 00:16:39.139
' Well, your flesh doesn't want to.

00:16:39.139 --> 00:16:41.200
'Well, it's all right to sleep around.

00:16:41.200 --> 00:16:43.900
It's all right to drink.

00:16:43.900 --> 00:16:45.519
It's all right to party.

00:16:45.519 --> 00:16:48.480
It's all right to do all these things.

00:16:48.480 --> 00:16:51.280
We're not going to judge you.

00:16:51.280 --> 00:16:53.097
' Are you serious?

00:16:53.097 --> 00:16:55.680
We're going to walk in grace and mercy.

00:17:07.383 --> 00:17:07.714
I'm going to tell you this: you are either hot for Jesus or cold.

00:17:07.714 --> 00:17:12.666
If you're lukewarm, He'll spew you out of His mouth.

00:17:15.109 --> 00:17:19.679
And people who think they can live a compromising lifestyle and make it in the rapture, you have another thing coming.

00:17:19.679 --> 00:17:25.280
So many of you are going to be taken aback by what's about to take place.

00:17:25.280 --> 00:17:29.200
A great shaking to awaken is coming.

00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:36.133
You're not going to live like the world and be a purified bride that's going to come and go in the rapture.

00:17:36.133 --> 00:17:42.000
There were five that had their lamps full and five that didn't.

00:17:42.000 --> 00:17:42.540
Which one are you?

00:17:46.079 --> 00:17:46.319
So, that's what I had for you.

00:17:46.319 --> 00:17:56.667
I just want you to get on fire for Jesus and know what's about to take place as we see all these major signs, as we see all this stuff going on.

00:17:56.667 --> 00:17:59.166
I'm just in awe that we're right there.

00:17:59.166 --> 00:18:01.760
We're seeing the covenant with many.

00:18:01.760 --> 00:18:09.653
We're seeing it talked about.

00:18:09.653 --> 00:18:22.746
We're seeing all these things, the red heifer and all this stuff.

00:18:22.746 --> 00:18:36.198
And I'm like, 'Wow, folks, this is so cool.

00:18:36.198 --> 00:18:54.080
' I'm excited about the prayer conference in the fall.

00:18:54.080 --> 00:19:17.235
Sister Billye always holds her prayer conference in the fall in October in Branson.

00:19:17.235 --> 00:19:43.052
And the Lord keeps showing me Branson for the major revival.

00:20:14.160 --> 00:20:14.827
I kept seeing visions of Branson today, and the leaves are still on the trees.

00:20:14.827 --> 00:20:24.469
It was beautiful outside, and there was an anticipation for something amazing about to take place in Branson, Missouri.

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:29.164
And then we have our prayer conference in Branson, Missouri, in October.

00:20:29.164 --> 00:20:35.176
We always do with Sister Billye.

00:20:35.176 --> 00:20:44.240
We go to that, and it's always such a blessing.

00:20:44.240 --> 00:20:52.754
It's one of my favorite things to do in October.

00:20:52.754 --> 00:20:56.319
I think it's like the 15th or something.

00:20:56.319 --> 00:21:03.260
So I always encourage people to come and help her be a part of a prayer meeting.

00:21:03.260 --> 00:21:08.400
You know, what are we expecting in these last days?

00:21:08.400 --> 00:21:42.010
Last year when we prayed, the Lord said, 'You've delayed the financial crisis for this four-year window—or it was a four-year, now three-year window.

00:21:42.010 --> 00:21:49.209
' And He said, 'You've delayed things that were coming to pass.

00:21:49.209 --> 00:21:58.613
Now you've delayed it because of the prayers of the righteous people interceding for America.

00:21:58.613 --> 00:22:00.640
You've delayed things.

00:22:00.640 --> 00:22:05.679
I'm giving you a window of time.

